# ðŸŽ¨ UI Components Guide

This guide explains the key UI components used in Wallet UI, built with React and Tailwind CSS.

---

## ðŸ”˜ ConnectWalletButton

- Triggers wallet connection using Crypto SDK
- Displays connected wallet address
- Shows loading and error states

### Props:
```ts
interface ConnectWalletButtonProps {
  onConnect: () => void;
  isConnected: boolean;
  address?: string;
}
interface BalanceCardProps {
  balance: number;
  currency: 'BTC' | 'ETH' | 'USD';
  fiatRate?: number;
}
interface TransactionListProps {
  transactions: Transaction[];
  onFilterChange: (filter: FilterOptions) => void;
}
interface ExchangeModalProps {
  fromCurrency: string;
  toCurrency: string;
  amount: number;
  onExchange: () => void;
}
interface SendReceiveModalProps {
  type: 'send' | 'receive';
  address: string;
  amount: number;
  onConfirm: () => void;
}
